snippet.title: Animal Songs: "Big Brown Boogieing Bear," by StoryBots | Netflix Jr
snippet.description:
What weighs 500 pounds and has the hottest dance moves in the forest? It's Big Brown Boogieing Bear!

The StoryBots are curious little creatures who live beneath our screens, offering a world of learning and fun for kids. The Emmy Award-winning “Ask the StoryBots” is now streaming on Netflix!

Lyrics:
Big Brown Boogieing Bear

Way out in the wilderness
Away from the city air
Bopping along with the forest song
It's the big brown boogieing bear

Well, the deer they can't stop laughing
And the birds all stop and stare
In the meadow green, it's quite a scene
He's the big brown boogieing bear

Big brown boogieing bear
Big brown boogieing bear
Gotta be around 500 pounds
Of wiggling jiggling hair!

Big brown boogieing bear
Big brown boogieing bear
You'll lose your frown when you're boogieing down
with the big brown boogieing bear

All winter he's been sleeping
Hibernating in his lair
Now skies are blue, so it's time to groove
For that big brown boogieing bear

Next time you're out in nature
And you hear beat from over there
Beyond the trees you just might see
That big brown boogieing bear

He's a big brown boogieing bear

That big brown boogieing bear!
